    Phase 2 - Monitoring & Logging enhancements to add:
    - CloudWatch alarms for EC2, RDS, ALB metrics
    - CloudWatch dashboards
    - SNS topics for alerting
    - Enhanced CloudWatch agent on EC2 instances
